Enum WebConfigKeys

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WebConfigKeys>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WebConfigKeys>

    public enum WebConfigKeys
extends java.lang.Enum<WebConfigKeys>
    List of all property keys authorized for a webapp configuration based on a properties file.
